Modify the clearContainer method in the TabbedFileEditor class.
Make it so that it sets the container height and width to 100%. 

Remember to respond with a snippet in the form of the following:
```
class TabbedFileEditor {
    clearContainer() {
        // your code here
    }
}
```

```javascript
class TabbedFileEditor {
    clearContainer() {
        this.container.innerHTML = '';
        this.container.style.height = '100%';
        this.container.style.width = '100%';
    }
}
```
